org.accada.epcis.queryclient
Class QueryClientGuiHelper

java.lang.Object
  org.accada.epcis.queryclient.QueryClientGuiHelper

public class QueryClientGuiHelper
extends java.lang.Object

Implements a Class to interface with the axis stubs for the EPCIS Query Interface. Also offers some helper methods to convert between different formats and for debug output.

Author:
David Gubler
